<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Reconix Scan Engine Report - {{ report.target_url }}</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #f4f7fb;
    --surface: #ffffff;
    --panel: #f8fafc;
    --border: #dce4ee;
    --text: #0f172a;
    --muted: #64748b;
    --critical: #dc2626;
    --high: #ea580c;
    --medium: #d97706;
    --low: #2563eb;
    --info: #64748b;
    --accent: #0f766e;
  }
  @page { size: A4; margin: 12mm; }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }
  .page {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 28px 32px 40px;
    background: var(--surface);
  }
  .header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #2563eb 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 22px 24px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  h1 { font-size: 26px; margin: 0 0 6px; }
  .header-meta { font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.95; }
  h2 {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin: 26px 0 12px;
    padding-bottom: 6px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: #0f172a;
  }
  h3 { font-size: 15px; margin: 8px 0 6px; }
  .hero-card {
    background: var(--panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .summary-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .stat-card {
    background: var(--panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-value { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
  .stat-card.critical .stat-value { color: var(--critical); }
  .stat-card.high .stat-value { color: var(--high); }
  .stat-card.medium .stat-value { color: var(--medium); }
  .stat-card.low .stat-value { color: var(--low); }
  .stat-card.info .stat-value { color: var(--info); }
  .stat-card.risk .stat-value { color: var(--accent); }
  .kv { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin: 6px 0; }
  .kv b { color: var(--text); }
  .recommendations {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #eff6ff 0%, #f8fafc 100%);
    border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
  }
  .recommendations ul { margin: 6px 0 0 18px; padding: 0; }
  .recommendations li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .finding-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--info);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 16px 16px 12px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
    break-inside: avoid;
  }
  .finding-card.critical { border-left-color: var(--critical); }
  .finding-card.high { border-left-color: var(--high); }
  .finding-card.medium { border-left-color: var(--medium); }
  .finding-card.low { border-left-color: var(--low); }
  .finding-card.info { border-left-color: var(--info); }
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-right: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .badge.critical { background: rgba(220,38,38,0.12); color: var(--critical); }
  .badge.high { background: rgba(234,88,12,0.12); color: var(--high); }
  .badge.medium { background: rgba(217,119,6,0.12); color: var(--medium); }
  .badge.low { background: rgba(37,99,235,0.12); color: var(--low); }
  .badge.info { background: rgba(100,116,139,0.12); color: var(--info); }
  .badge.fp-warning { background: rgba(217,119,6,0.16); color: var(--medium); }
  code, pre {
    background: #f8fafc;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 8px 10px;
    font-family: "SFMono-Regular", Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    word-break: break-all;
    display: block;
  }
  .section-label { font-weight: 700; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 3px; font-size: 13px; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 12.5px; margin-top: 10px; }
  th, td { border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 6px 8px; text-align: left; }
  th { background: var(--panel); color: var(--muted); }
  tr:nth-child(even) { background: rgba(15,23,42,0.02); }
  .footer { margin-top: 36px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
  <div class="header">
    <div class="eyebrow">Professional Security Assessment</div>
    <h1>Reconix Scan Report</h1>
    <div class="header-meta">
      <b>Target:</b> {{ report.target_url }} &middot;
      <b>Scan ID:</b> {{ report.scan_id }} &middot;
      <b>Generated:</b> {{ report.generated_at }}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-card">
    <h2>Executive Summary</h2>
    <p>This report provides a concise, executive-level view of the security posture for the scanned target. It highlights severity trends, primary risk areas, and clear follow-up actions for remediation and retesting.</p>
    <div class="summary-grid">
      <div class="stat-card risk"><div class="stat-value">{{ report.summary.risk_score }}</div><div class="stat-label">Risk Score</div></div>
      <div class="stat-card critical"><div class="stat-value">{{ report.summary.critical_count }}</div><div class="stat-label">Critical</div></div>
      <div class="stat-card high"><div class="stat-value">{{ report.summary.high_count }}</div><div class="stat-label">High</div></div>
      <div class="stat-card medium"><div class="stat-value">{{ report.summary.medium_count }}</div><div class="stat-label">Medium</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="kv" style="margin-top:12px;">
      <b>{{ report.summary.pages_crawled }}</b> pages crawled &middot;
      <b>{{ report.summary.endpoints_discovered }}</b> endpoints discovered &middot;
      <b>{{ report.summary.total_findings }}</b> total findings
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Recommended Next Steps</h2>
  <div class="recommendations">
    <ul>
      {% if report.summary.critical_count > 0 %}<li>Prioritize remediation for critical vulnerabilities and restrict public access until they are validated and mitigated.</li>{% endif %}
      {% if report.summary.high_count > 0 %}<li>Address high-severity findings as part of the next remediation sprint and verify the fixes with follow-up testing.</li>{% endif %}
      {% if report.summary.medium_count > 0 or report.summary.low_count > 0 %}<li>Review medium and low severity weaknesses to harden the application and reduce long-term exposure.</li>{% endif %}
      {% if report.findings %}<li>Retest the affected endpoints after remediation and preserve evidence in the audit trail for review and compliance.</li>{% endif %}
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h2>Findings</h2>
  {% if not report.findings %}
    <p>No findings were reported for this scan.</p>
  {% endif %}
  {% for f in report.findings %}
  <div class="finding-card {{ f.severity }}">
    <div>
      <span class="badge {{ f.severity }}">{{ f.severity }}</span>
      {% if f.is_likely_false_positive %}<span class="badge fp-warning">verify: low confidence</span>{% endif %}
    </div>
    <h3>{{ loop.index }}. {{ f.title }}</h3>
    <div class="kv"><b>URL:</b> {{ f.method }} {{ f.url }}</div>
    <div class="kv"><b>Parameter:</b> {{ f.parameter or "N/A" }}</div>
    <div class="kv"><b>OWASP:</b> {{ f.owasp_category }}</div>
    <div class="kv"><b>CVSS:</b> {{ f.cvss_score }}{% if f.cvss_vector %} ({{ f.cvss_vector }}){% endif %}</div>
    <div class="kv"><b>Confidence:</b> {{ "%.2f"|format(f.confidence) }} ({{ f.confidence_band }})</div>

    <div class="section-label">Evidence</div>
    <div>{{ f.evidence }}</div>

    <div class="section-label">Risk Explanation</div>
    <div>{{ f.risk_explanation }}</div>

    <div class="section-label">Business Impact</div>
    <div>{{ f.business_impact }}</div>

    <div class="section-label">Remediation</div>
    <div style="white-space: pre-line;">{{ f.remediation }}</div>

    {% if f.safe_poc %}
    <div class="section-label">Safe Proof of Concept</div>
    <div class="kv"><b>Request</b></div>
    <pre>{{ f.safe_poc.example_request }}</pre>
    <div class="kv"><b>Example vulnerable response</b></div>
    <pre>{{ f.safe_poc.example_response }}</pre>
    <div class="kv"><b>Expected safe output:</b> {{ f.safe_poc.expected_safe_output }}</div>
    <div class="kv"><b>Impact:</b> {{ f.safe_poc.impact }}</div>
    <div class="kv"><b>Verification steps:</b></div>
    <ol>
      {% for step in f.safe_poc.verification_steps %}<li>{{ step }}</li>{% endfor %}
    </ol>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  {% endfor %}

  <h2>Audit Trail</h2>
  <div class="kv">{{ report.audit_trail|length }} requests logged (showing most recent 50).</div>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Timestamp</th><th>Module</th><th>Method</th><th>URL</th><th>Status</th><th>Duration (ms)</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {% for entry in report.audit_trail[-50:] %}
      <tr>
        <td>{{ entry.timestamp }}</td>
        <td>{{ entry.module }}</td>
        <td>{{ entry.method }}</td>
        <td>{{ entry.url }}</td>
        <td>{{ entry.response_code or "-" }}</td>
        <td>{{ "%.1f"|format(entry.duration_ms) }}</td>
      </tr>
      {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <div class="footer">
    Generated by Reconix Scan Engine &middot; Defensive, educational vulnerability scanning &middot;
    All proof-of-concept content in this report is safe and non-destructive.
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>